#: ../../docs/documentation_guidelines/writing.rst:296
msgid ""
"To avoid conflicts with other references, always begin figure anchors with "
"``_figure_`` and use terms that easily connect to the figure caption. While "
"only the centered alignment is mandatory for the image, feel free to use any"
" other options for figures (such as ``width``, ``height``, ``scale``...) if "
"needed."
